{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act21side", "eventName": "敘拉古人", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "IS-5", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "恆久法則", "storyInfo": "瓦拉赫憤怒於德克薩斯的選擇，拉維妮婭提出要見貝納爾多，準備質問他的選擇。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "33_g7_reception", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$drift_intro", "key": "$drift_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_695_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然我也考慮過萊昂圖索在誆我的可能性，但是，一見到你我就知道了。", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#5$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是貨真價實的德克薩斯。", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#5$1"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_695_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "德克薩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_695_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "容我自我介紹一下，我是羅塞蒂家族的瓦拉赫。", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#5$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_695_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是哥倫比亞人？", "name": "德克薩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_695_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，羅塞蒂家族的大部分成員都是哥倫比亞人。", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#5$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_695_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如何，這裡的監獄生活？", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#5$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_695_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒什麼特別的。", "name": "德克薩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#8$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_695_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真奇怪，照理說，你不應該在監獄裡待這麼久，貝洛內到底是怎麼想的。", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#5$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_695_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "遵紀守法，很奇怪嗎？", "name": "德克薩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_695_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "遵紀守法？但是敘拉古的法院，跟所謂的法律真的有關係嗎？", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#5$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "比如，在大部分的敘拉古城市，一個家族成員的成年禮，就是上一次法庭，進一次監獄。", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#5$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後，他的家族成員會像迎接一名戰士一樣，將他帶回家族。", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#5$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個國家表面上的一切，對我們這種身處地下秩序的人來說，都形同虛設。", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#5$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_695_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以呢？", "name": "德克薩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_695_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是在哥倫比亞長大的人，難道還需要我來解釋嗎？", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#5$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“可笑”，我沒有除此以外的評價。", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#5$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，也拜此所賜，我們才能夠如此順利地在這裡扎根。", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#5$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_695_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你很喜歡和人聊政治嗎？", "name": "德克薩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_695_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來你不喜歡。", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#5$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其實我也不喜歡。", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#5$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我就直說吧，你為什麼沒有死？", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "與你無關。", "name": "德克薩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好吧，那我換個問法，你為什麼要回來？", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊昂圖索沒有告訴你嗎？我欠貝洛內一次。", "name": "德克薩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，我是不是可以理解為，你知道貝洛內是為了讓你對付我們羅塞蒂才讓你回來的，你還是回來了。", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也是回來之後才知道的，不過——你確實可以這麼理解。", "name": "德克薩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的坦誠甚至讓我懷疑是不是我出了問題，最後的德克薩斯。", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道你要告訴我，你已經完全忘記了，德克薩斯這個姓氏曾經統領著哥倫比亞大大小小的家族？", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_695_1#4$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的爺爺，薩爾瓦多雷曾經是每一個哥倫比亞家族成員的信仰？！", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#4$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_695_1#4$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "德克薩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#8$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "德克薩斯留下的一切，都與我無關。", "name": "德克薩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#8$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "都與你無關？！", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_smashtable", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$blooddrop", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "瓦拉赫一拳打在旁邊的茶几上，鮮血從手指上流了下來。"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而他彷彿渾然未覺。"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_695_1#4$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是切利尼娜·德克薩斯！薩爾瓦多雷的孫女！", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#4$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你只要活著，那些東西就與你有關！", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#4$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "光是你的名字出現在羅塞蒂的會議桌上，就會讓我們不得不去改變行動的方針！", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#4$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們曾經以德克薩斯為榮！", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#4$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為了不讓薩爾瓦多雷的心血白費，你知不知道，喬萬娜花了多少力氣才將剩下的哥倫比亞家族重新統合起來？", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你知不知道，我們如何向西西里夫人卑躬屈膝，最終選擇向敘拉古回流，從哥倫比亞千里迢迢返回敘拉古？", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為了生存，我們甚至將建造移動城市的技術和盤托出，幾乎在免費為敘拉古建造新的移動城市——", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這一切都是因為德克薩斯的隕落，我們不得不接受了這個事實。", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而現在，你，最後的德克薩斯，堂而皇之地踏上了這片土地。", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卻說你與這一切無關，你只是來還債。", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_695_1#4$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你甚至站在了我們的對立面！", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#4$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你欠貝洛內的？", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#4$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然你活著，那你欠哥倫比亞家族的更多！", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#4$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_695_1#4$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我或許欠喬萬娜一個交代，但我不欠哥倫比亞家族的。", "name": "德克薩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "完成和貝洛內的約定後，我會離開敘拉古。", "name": "德克薩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你覺得我會相信嗎？", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的存在，就是對羅塞蒂根基的動搖。", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "德克薩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喬萬娜呢？", "name": "德克薩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼？", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我問，為什麼是你來見我，而不是喬萬娜。", "name": "德克薩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是她的代言人。", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她不會說，向西西里夫人卑躬屈膝。", "name": "德克薩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她也不會派一個使者來見我。", "name": "德克薩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你以為你瞭解她？", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從你的表現來看，或許是這樣。", "name": "德克薩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_695_1#3$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊......真可惜。", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#3$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來，我還是不夠瞭解傳聞中的德克薩斯。", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#3$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_695_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還以為我的演技不錯。", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#5$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_695_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不算差。", "name": "德克薩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#8$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是，你高談闊論著敘拉古，彷彿已經看穿了這個國家的樣子，讓我覺得......很熟悉。", "name": "德克薩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#8$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_695_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不推薦你這麼做。", "name": "德克薩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_695_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼？", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#5$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_695_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為這意味著......你還不夠瞭解這個國家。", "name": "德克薩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，有一點你說得對，我既然回來了，應該和喬萬娜聊一聊。", "name": "德克薩斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你見不到她的。", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_shufflecards", "channel": "a", "loop": "true"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "a", "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_698_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_698_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不好意思，最後的德克薩斯。", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你太像一個敘拉古人了，不，你是一個徹頭徹尾的敘拉古人。", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，我不能讓你見首領。", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你會動搖她，你會動搖許多人，你會毀了許多東西。", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#1$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_695_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，請回吧。", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#4$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "去履行你和貝洛內的約定吧，然後，滾回你苟且偷生的地方。", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#4$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你想做什麼都是你的自由。", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#4$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，唯獨有一點，請你記住。", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#4$1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "羅塞蒂家族，不歡迎你。", "name": "瓦拉赫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_695_1#4$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 5.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 10.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "德克薩斯站起身，向門口走去。"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_698_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_698_1#1$1", "fadetime": 0.3}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "xpos": 150.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "殺手們不自覺地為她讓出一條道路。"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她環視一圈，從這些哥倫比亞人的眼中讀出了憤怒，不解，厭惡，困惑等等情緒。"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就是這個姓氏帶來的東西。"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "德克薩斯。"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她歎了口氣，走出房間。"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "33_g11_mansionhall", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_dooropen", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4065_judge_1#7$1", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_690_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "稀客。", "name": "德米特里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_690_1#1$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4065_judge_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我要見貝納爾多。", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#7$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_690_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我提醒過你很多次，不要直呼首領的名字，拉維妮婭小姐。", "name": "德米特里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_690_1#9$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4065_judge_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你知道他在哪，對嗎？", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#7$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_690_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我有什麼理由必須告訴你嗎？", "name": "德米特里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_690_1#9$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4065_judge_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果我現在站在這裡，聽完你作為勝利者的嘲諷，可以讓你告訴我的話，我不在乎。", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#7$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_690_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "勝利者......", "name": "德米特里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_690_1#8$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_690_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "算了。", "name": "德米特里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_690_1#9$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "告訴你也無妨，首領已經啟程去薩盧佐家族的宅邸了。", "name": "德米特里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_690_1#9$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你見不到他的。", "name": "德米特里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_690_1#9$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你想在這座宅子怎麼鬧，都是你的事。", "name": "德米特里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_690_1#9$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，首領既然決定去和薩盧佐家談，那麼，我勸你不要做多餘的事。", "name": "德米特里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_690_1#9$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4065_judge_1#8$1", "name2": "char_empty"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "xpos": 200.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_690_1#9$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1", "name2": "char_empty"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "xpos": 200.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用你提醒我。", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_690_1#9$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_690_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以及，拉維妮婭小姐。", "name": "德米特里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_690_1#1$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_690_1#9$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你怎麼看待我，我並不在乎。", "name": "德米特里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_690_1#9$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，我希望你不要忘記。", "name": "德米特里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_690_1#9$1"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊昂是這個家族的一員，是他偏離了家族應有的軌道在先。", "name": "德米特里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_690_1#9$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們是一個家族，一個家族應當齊心協力。", "name": "德米特里"}, "figure_art": "avg_